review: Would have helped if the approach was positive. Have consulted other orthos in the past but this by far is one of my low experiences.
reply_text:
Expectation is a very subjective thing. I give a balanced opinion. I do not give a false positive opinion just to please a patient. If you want to discuss the specifics of your case, you are welcome to see me again since I do not know who you are or what your problem was (your details are not visible in the feedback). 

A doctor-patient interaction is a two-way street. If you found the interaction not to your liking, chances are, I also must have had negative vibes from you.
